<h2 id="tracking-results">Tracking Sales Performance</h2>

<div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none">

You can't improve what you don't measure. Track these key metrics to optimize your sales training program:

**Individual Technician Metrics:**
- Average ticket size (target: 40-60% increase from baseline)
- Close rate on presented options (target: 60-70%)
- Maintenance agreement sales rate (target: 35-45%)
- Customer satisfaction scores (maintain above 4.5/5)

**Company-Wide Metrics:**
- Overall revenue per service call
- Maintenance agreement recurring revenue
- Customer lifetime value
- Technician confidence scores (measured quarterly)

**Using CRM Data for Sales Coaching:**

Modern HVAC software tracks detailed sales metrics. Use this data to identify top performers and coach struggling technicians. For example, if one technician has a 75% close rate while another has 35%, analyze their approaches and share best practices.

